		<articleText><![CDATA[<p>Thank you for taking the time to look at our new edge series template!  The new edge series of templates are a result of hundreds of hours and months of development. Our previous template, Unlimited, was released in August of 2009 and currently has been purchased close to 600 times. Countless hundreds of you web developers out there posted on our forum letting us know what you liked and didn't like and what you would like to potentially see changed or added.  So we listened, sorted out the most common requests, and added as many new features as we possibly could and then a couple more. Some of the big features you guys requested the most were:  Being able to change page name and page title for deeplinking from XML.  Disable/Enable Mp3 player from XML.  Make navigation buttons resize based on the length of the text length. Position header, navigation, and nav buttons from XML. Load full size scaled images as backgrounds. Load swfs and videos as backgrounds. And we added all of these plus a TON more!  Hope you guys enjoy this template! Due to the hundreds of new XML options we have added, you will be able to skin this template to your likings 10 times faster than before!</p>]]></articleText>
